OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'erasing Jewish
OL,4,Cidentity' says Plymouth campaigner
OL,6,FSam Blackledge reports on concerns
OL,7,Fabout rising antisemitic hate crime
OL,9,FHate crimes against Jewish people are
OL,10,Fincreasing across Devon and Cornwall,
OL,11,Faccording to figures from the region's
OL,12,Fpolice force.
OL,14,FA campaigner who supports victims in
OL,15,FPlymouth is now calling on the police
OL,16,Fto take the issue more seriously.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
