CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778677871
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'erasing Jewish
OL,4,Cidentity' says Plymouth campaigner
OL,6,FTom Godwin, who runs the Plymouth
OL,7,FJewish Community CIC, said: "Many
OL,8,Fpeople in the region have never met
OL,9,Fsomeone Jewish, they've never
OL,10,Funderstood what it means to be Jewish,
OL,11,Fto be connected to a people and a
OL,12,Fstory.
OL,14,F"Even if you're not religiously
OL,15,FJewish, you're born into a cultural
OL,16,Fset of norms. We are seeing a kind of
OL,17,Ferasure of Jewish identity, where
OL,18,Fpeople don't feel able to even wear
OL,19,Ftheir Magen David around their neck in
OL,20,Fpublic.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778677871
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'erasing Jewish
OL,4,Cidentity' says Plymouth campaigner
OL,6,F"People not feeling safe to share
OL,7,Ftheir Jewish identity, students taking
OL,8,Ftheir mezuzahs down, not congregating
OL,9,Fat Jewish events, and 92 per cent of
OL,10,Fthe cases we've supported with have
OL,11,Fnot reported to the police.
OL,13,F"So there's a bigger problem than
OL,14,Fpeople are aware of."
OL,16,FDevon and Cornwall Police has recorded
OL,17,Fmore than 200 hate crimes linked to
OL,18,FJewish people or antisemitism over the
OL,19,Fpast five years.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
