FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778677871
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'erasing Jewish
OL,4,Cidentity' says Plymouth campaigner
OL,6,FLast year alone, these included
OL,7,Fcriminal damage; stalking and
OL,8,Fharassment; violence; burglary; and
OL,9,Fpublic order offences.
OL,11,FTom says his work in the community has
OL,12,Fshown him that hate can come in many
OL,13,Fforms.
OL,15,F"People avoid the city centre on
OL,16,Fcertain days for fear of being
OL,17,Fverbally chastised in the street," he
OL,18,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778677871
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'erasing Jewish
OL,4,Cidentity' says Plymouth campaigner
OL,6,F"It's more insidious as well. I know
OL,7,Fthat appearing on your programme will
OL,8,Flead to a series of e-mails. We take
OL,9,Fsteps to counter that."
OL,11,FRabbi Mendy Singer says the rise in
OL,12,Fantisemitism is a sign of an
OL,13,Fincreasingly fractured society.
OL,15,F"Anti-semitism is not a new issue," he
OL,16,Fsaid. "But it's definitely been
OL,17,Fexacerbated.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778677871
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'erasing Jewish
OL,4,Cidentity' says Plymouth campaigner
OL,6,F"I'm a Rabbi, I don't get involved in
OL,7,Fpolitics, and I think ultimately anti-
OL,8,Fsemitism isn't really a Jewish
OL,9,Fproblem. Because the Jews are just the
OL,10,Ffirst.
OL,12,F"It's an early warning sign. A society
OL,13,Fthat can't protect its Jewish
OL,14,Fcommunities ends up facing greater
OL,15,Fissues.
OL,17,F"I think this should be wake-up call,
OL,18,Fif it isn't already, for the
OL,19,Fauthorities and powers that be to
OL,20,Fperhaps address this more seriously
OL,21,Fthan they already are."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
