CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778677871
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'erasing Jewish
OL,4,Cidentity' says Plymouth campaigner
OL,6,FDevon and Cornwall Police recorded 56
OL,7,Fantisemitic crimes in the 12 months up
OL,8,Fto 31 March 2026, compared to 36
OL,9,Fcrimes the previous year.
OL,11,FA spokesman for Devon and Cornwall
OL,12,FPolice said: "We recognise that the
OL,13,FGolders Green attack will have had a
OL,14,Fsignificant impact on Jewish
OL,15,Fcommunities here in Devon and Cornwall.
OL,17,F"During times of tension, we gather
OL,18,Fdaily intelligence to understand local
OL,19,Fthreats and concerns so that we can
OL,20,Frespond effectively and support
OL,21,Faffected communities.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778677871
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'erasing Jewish
OL,4,Cidentity' says Plymouth campaigner
OL,6,F"Our specialist Diverse Communities
OL,7,FTeam and neighbourhood officers are
OL,8,Fregularly engaging with Jewish
OL,9,Fcommunities and synagogues throughout
OL,10,Four area to provide reassurance and to
OL,11,Flisten to concerns."
OL,13,FThey added: "We know that hate crime
OL,14,Fgoes unreported and it is highly
OL,15,Flikely that the rise we have seen
OL,16,Freflects an increase in incidents,
OL,17,Frather than solely confidence in
OL,18,Freporting.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778677871
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'erasing Jewish
OL,4,Cidentity' says Plymouth campaigner
OL,6,F"We do not tolerate hate crime in any
OL,7,Fform and strongly encourage victims to
OL,8,Fcome forward and report incidents to
OL,9,Fus, safe in the knowledge that we will
OL,10,Ftake them seriously and thoroughly
OL,11,Finvestigate any offences.
OL,13,F"Later this month our Plymouth police
OL,14,Fcommander and the force lead for hate
OL,15,Fcrime will be meeting with
OL,16,Frepresentatives of Plymouth Jewish
OL,17,FCommunity CIC and Community Security
OL,18,FTrust to explore ways in which we
OL,19,Fincrease trust and encourage reporting
OL,20,Fwithin the Jewish community in
OL,21,FPlymouth."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778677871
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'erasing Jewish
OL,4,Cidentity' says Plymouth campaigner
OL,6,FAlison Hernandez, Devon and Cornwall's
OL,7,FPolice and Crime Commissioner, added:
OL,8,F"It's so important that if people have
OL,9,Fbeen affected by an incident of hate
OL,10,Fin their community, that they report
OL,11,Fit to the police.
OL,13,F"I want people to be assured that the
OL,14,Fpolice do take it seriously and if
OL,15,Fthey don't feel they have, they can
OL,16,Fcome to my office and that's what I'm
OL,17,Fhere for.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
