PN,43511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1778677871
OL,3,CAntisemitism is 'erasing Jewish
OL,4,Cidentity' says Plymouth campaigner
OL,6,F"It's really important to reassure all
OL,7,Fcommunities that anyone who has been a
OL,8,Fvictim of crime, but particularly one
OL,9,Fthat may be targeted at them
OL,10,Fpersonally and it's regarded as hate,
OL,11,Fis taken very seriously."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/11
